<div id="outline-container-orgaba6eab" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgaba6eab">boxplot</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgaba6eab">
<p>
は複数のベクトル中に含まれる値の分布を表す箱ひげ図を作成します。
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-R"><span style="color: #99968b;">##</span>
<span style="color: #99968b;">## </span><span style="color: #99968b;">12.4 &#31665;&#12498;&#12466;&#22259;</span>
<span style="color: #99968b;">##</span>

x1 <span style="color: #e5786d;">&lt;-</span> c(11,12,11,10,11,11,12,13,15,12,11,10,12,13)
x2 <span style="color: #e5786d;">&lt;-</span> c(20,21,27,9,12,23,23,12,11,9,21,15,7,12,12,9,23,15)
boxplot(x1, x2, names=c(<span style="color: #95e454;">"Data 1"</span>, <span style="color: #95e454;">"Data 2"</span>))

</pre>
</div>


